        <num>CC 3166</num>
        <heading>3166.  Modification as default by pledgor</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3166.  Modification as default by pledgor
The pledgor and pledgee may agree that a modification or termination of the contract
from which a pledged obligation of a third person arises, or the substitution of a new
contract, is a default by the pledgor.</p>
        </content>
